{"tid":433863,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有個臭西港女性格既家姐真係慘過食兩舊屎","createTime":"2017-10-12T17:37:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-12T22:38:58.000Z","uid":56047,"like":35,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"57ba5ac26c873065de0dd4590a7b9c54c85027f3","tid":433863,"uid":56047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T17:37:37.000Z","msg":"說話細佬我岩岩放工<br />\n番到屋企一陣 就去左沖涼<br />\n沖左十分鍾家姐就拍門話<br />\n我:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n家姐:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :你沖完未呀!我要去廁所之後訓教呀!<br />\n咁我沖多五分鍾 <br />\n沖完出黎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :喂 好心你係我一開始沖涼既時候就話要去廁所啦<br />\n次次都係我沖到一半既時候就係到拍門               <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :咁我用緊電腦吖嘛 唔知你沖涼 你沖涼之前又唔講<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :吓!?咁我洗唔洗做咩都要同你講吖?<br />\n咁樣就開始嘈 講到我好似要老溤要提佢咁<br />\n冇提係我錯咁<br />\n之後我家姐就好嬲咁走左去訓教 我過左陣就問佢 都唔知你嬲乜 <br />\n佢冇理我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我之後send whatapp解釋成個對話 話我冇責任要提佢要去廁所乜乜乜<br />\n如果咁樣咁樣講就唔會嘈交<br />\n以上係我同家姐間唔中會發生既事<br />\n我最近先發覺我家姐好港女性格 開始頂佢唔順<br />\n各位巴打覺得我要點做<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  :以後冇撚理你 當佢透明<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :聽日同佢SAY sorry"},{"pid":"853630933ef80a7947b099a15499bbc201bc2521","tid":433863,"uid":137233,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T17:38:49.000Z","msg":"係我就屌柒佢"},{"pid":"350ed88bd9b2be726568a55a57fbd938e2a904c6","tid":433863,"uid":113465,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T17:39:49.000Z","msg":"你家姐又唔一早涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最撚憎呢啲人"},{"pid":"68363f574f6f751008873e9a9ced7b6c46d9a203","tid":433863,"uid":56047,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T17:45:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你家姐又唔一早涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最撚憎呢啲人</blockquote><br />\n佢唔係想去沖涼 佢係想柯尿訓教<br />\n我平日都會特登笠住條毛巾出黎等佢去先<br />\n但係佢今日個語氣好撚黑人憎 話咩我特登唔提佢去廁所 都痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45d548f69bb851c937dc88ad4f034c371a7db9de","tid":433863,"uid":145959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T17:45:20.000Z","msg":"幫佢執劑"},{"pid":"a87ff781a8eef9e0238b51aa98f9afeed587861e","tid":433863,"uid":109042,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T17:46:45.000Z","msg":"男朋友家姐又係成日唔一早沖涼等佢11點幾返黎就即刻攞衫去沖涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 或者有時做完運動一返到黎想即刻沖佢又入撚左去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 10次有8次都咁"},{"pid":"15d8cd8f29fbf4dac3aefc031ac7bab24ab799a6","tid":433863,"uid":7318,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T17:47:16.000Z","msg":"沖完涼出嚟講完<br />\nWhatsapp又講<br />\n似你想聊交打喎"},{"pid":"729ebd1a2ef5f19f2448351f545d6bf76012d581","tid":433863,"uid":56047,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T17:52:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>沖完涼出嚟講完<br />\nWhatsapp又講<br />\n似你想聊交打喎</blockquote><br />\n咁即係唔好理佢?<br />\n定係沖涼前老溤要提佢去廁所?"},{"pid":"15fffb80d9c6b596789b3bec27893a89ccb60106","tid":433863,"uid":56047,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T17:54:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>沖完涼出嚟講完<br />\nWhatsapp又講<br />\n似你想聊交打喎</blockquote><br />\n咁即係唔好理佢?<br />\n定係<span style=\"color: red;\">以後</span>沖涼前老溤要提佢去廁所?</blockquote>"},{"pid":"ff92653c2e1fdb0cd666dbc67536cedde21e7ba6","tid":433863,"uid":23727,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T18:07:06.000Z","msg":"咁似我家姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 已經老馮左每次屙屎沖涼之前都會問佢洗唔洗用廁所先